* In episode 4, The members of the '''Yukhoe Rice Team''' each won an Individual Ranking +1. * In episode 6, The members of the '''Ji! Seo! He!''', '''Hush''' '''Team''', '''By Collecting Dreams''' and '''Forever Love Team''' each won an Individual Ranking +3. '''Park So-myeong''' won Individual Ranking of +6 as Most Improved Student, hence she was tied 6th with Yoo Ji-na who had no ranking boosts. * In episode 7, '''Song Ha-young''' and '''Lee Sae-rom''' won the 2nd live and Individual Ranking +1.
