==Awards and nominations==

===BMI Awards===
The '''[[BMI Awards]]''' are annual award ceremonies for songwriters in various genres organized by [[Broadcast Music, Inc.|Broadcast Music, Inc]].
Oakenfold won the Film Award for Music the 2001 [[movie]] Swordfish.

